    <li><a href="/package/feed-crawl">feed-crawl</a> library: Utility for fetching feeds with redirect info and HTML link detection (<a href="/packages/tag/library">library</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/mit">mit</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/text">text</a>)</li>
    <li><a href="/package/feed-gipeda">feed-gipeda</a> library, program and test: CI service around gipeda (<a href="/packages/tag/benchmarking">benchmarking</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/bsd3">bsd3</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/library">library</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/program">program</a>)</li>
    <li><a href="/package/feed-translator">feed-translator</a> program: Translate syndication feeds (<a href="/packages/tag/agpl">agpl</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/program">program</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/web">web</a>)</li>
    <li class="deprecated"><a href="/package/feed2lj">feed2lj</a> program: (unsupported) (<a href="/packages/tag/bsd3">bsd3</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/deprecated">deprecated</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/program">program</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/unclassified">unclassified</a>)</li>
    <li><a href="/package/feed2twitter">feed2twitter</a> library and program: Send posts from a feed to Twitter (<a href="/packages/tag/bsd3">bsd3</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/library">library</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/program">program</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/web">web</a>)</li>
    <li><a href="/package/feldspar-compiler">feldspar-compiler</a> library, tests and benchmark: Compiler for the Feldspar language (<a href="/packages/tag/benchmark">benchmark</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/bsd3">bsd3</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/compiler">compiler</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/library">library</a>)</li>
    <li><a href="/package/feldspar-language">feldspar-language</a> library and tests: A functional embedded language for DSP and parallelism (<a href="/packages/tag/bsd3">bsd3</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/language">language</a>, <a href="/packages/tag/library">library</a>)</li>
